title: Growing Up In A Musical Household -  Jimmy Heath
fulltitle: Growing Up In A Musical Household -  Jimmy Heath

description: An outtake from my new doc, "Passing the Torch."  Here, Jimmy Heath remembers growing up in 1940s Philadelphia, part of a musical house hold that include youngest brother Albert "Tootie" Heath, and older brother, Percy Heath.  To view on Amazon Prime:  https://www.amazon.com/Passing-Torch-Jimmy-Heath/dp/B071LFRQDF/ref=sr_1_1?ie=UTF8&qid=1499727832&sr=8-1&
